
*** TRON PROJECTS ***

This document lists all projects inside the tron repository.
For each project the following structure is shown: 

> project - library or executable 

- dependency 1
- dependency 2 
...

* lib description
* ...

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> talky - libtron_talky.so		

- log4cxx

* Defines a standard language for communication between robotic control processes. 
* Language divided in topics, categories and concepts.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tuly - libtron_tuly.so 		

* Library for utilities:
* string handling, file handling, thread management, brooks control classes ...

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> comy - libtron_comy.so 		

- libtron_tuly
- log4cxx

* Library for inter process communication.
* Should be extended with ZeroMQ library.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

> tron_test - tron_test 		

- libtron_talky
- libtron_tuly
- libtron_comy
- log4cxx

* Program used for testing all tron libs.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


